_sText:
This is the Counter-Strike Source version of the map fy_houses which I originally made for Counter-Strike. The new Source version now has 32 spawn points for maximum carnage. As the name implies, this is a fy style map with houses and plenty of guns.

Special thanks to Valve and Turtle Rock Studios for textures and inspiration.

cstrike-planet rocks!
